{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6236a37e-f591-4cd1-b97e-34d1adfdb480","content":"**No, you no longer need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`.** In .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` natively speaks the Microsoft.Testing.Platform protocol, so that bridge property is obsolete.\n\nYour only required property is `EnableMSTestRunner` (which you already have). Let me clean up your project file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01BGEMY3pNcs7nxxNBMwSeRb","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-66e43d807bca408f8145542ed4417e5c/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-66e43d807bca408f8145542ed4417e5c/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"2f7c6b38-82da-4864-91db-5983931eab10","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about native MTP support. Let me check the current state of .NET 10 regarding MTP.\n\nIn .NET 10, Microsoft made `dotnet test` natively support Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) without needing the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property. This was a key change - the new `dotnet test` integration was built directly into the SDK.\n\nKey points:\n1. In .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` uses MTP natively - the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property is no longer needed.\n\n\n2. Since they already have `EnableMSTestRunner` set to `true`, that's the right configuration for MTP. They can safely remove the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property since .NET 10 handles this automatically.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` was redesigned to natively support MTP, so that compatibility property isn't needed anymore. The new implementation automatically discovers and runs MTP-based test apps, though the legacy VSTest-based version is still available with the `--legacy` flag if needed.","outputTokens":771,"requestId":"7C39:156E46:140C6EB:1689CAD:69F940D7"},"id":"9a758083-cb88-42ab-bad5-cbe3f0f4492e","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:59:17.500Z","parentId":"f0bef692-fe8a-4c1e-8d65-c843b702de5b"}
